{"id": "6657687623b44b8c2a9753e2c762ced8bb73fa56b14511a29ca79db913ec5dfa", "item_id": "461c027c8a:0", "text": "Activate Interactive Denoising"}
{"id": "5800ba89ddf30298214b5a536422df2caad6791e480cce71f30885d36e184474", "item_id": "461c027c8a:1", "text": "The interactive denoising option can be found on the PrmanGlobalStatements node"}
{"id": "66962f72a08883733c35df6f82a049b929f9579f19c4bc083ac99bead602eab3", "item_id": "461c027c8a:2", "text": "Preferences"}
{"id": "b4913cc903d98bafc9962b20c21ebc2918e496b2e5dcb7fd610d83d90de0fa4c", "item_id": "461c027c8a:3", "text": "Cheap First Pass"}
{"id": "8a00bb66c3d3deb8e7f9d35851eaa37a9873e0014e62e2f750af48caa4912e9b", "item_id": "461c027c8a:4", "text": "If checked, the first pass will use a cheaper (slightly faster but lower quality) heuristic."}
{"id": "2cbd8c4f308a12fd4815a89e9242087039afb9475512b3a2fd65e6df40824862", "item_id": "461c027c8a:5", "text": "This can be useful if rendering something that is converging very quickly and you want to prioritize getting a denoised result faster."}
{"id": "6f45b0005e3b7c18ecd474b906b61876b7bb18e969e89d8728187e4417c364f8", "item_id": "461c027c8a:6", "text": "Interval"}
{"id": "42989d486135d6dfb1000903762e1e1c366824ffdec0b08e17cda9016dadfe87", "item_id": "461c027c8a:7", "text": "The time interval in between denoise runs (in seconds)"}
{"id": "5ec00a504f8c5412d5bd3e3d77d3ea5aec7a066e5afcd5ba5f1433124a8024bf", "item_id": "461c027c8a:8", "text": "LogInfo"}
{"id": "d9a567013fc58c30e42a0c0342658df590343bddf2bda61de6eefb1a11937443", "item_id": "461c027c8a:9", "text": "Output logging info"}
{"id": "7a16cc6510cf5d06f079003eb5badefe26d4a14d550ad1ae40936c05c583040f", "item_id": "461c027c8a:10", "text": "Min Samples"}
{"id": "8438dd91e874df0a7109c489563f63bb38a66d339677d1bcc1a843a9c07fbb25", "item_id": "461c027c8a:11", "text": "The minimum number of average samples per bucket before the interactive denoiser runs for the first time.  Changing this preference requires the render to be restarted for this option to be respected"}
{"id": "7d668e6c8c060f7820a4f1b517d9750ec4b9e171c42c13fa57c943892e6d8ee4", "item_id": "461c027c8a:12", "text": "Your browser does not support the HTML5 video element"}
